    Version: 1.0.2
    DisplayName: Deathwatch - Play as a Space Marine
    Description: Create and play a Deathwatch Space Marine in the base campaign.
      A fully converted character creator (Chapter, Speciality, Deed of Renown, Burden
      of Service), full-size armoured Astartes with per-Chapter heraldry, custom
      voices, and an Astartes arsenal. Requires the Infinite Museion DLC. Saves containing
      a marine require this mod; saves without one are unaffected.
